---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout
  title="About Me"
  description="Senior Software Engineer & Security Researcher"
>
  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2>Summary</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      I'm deeply involved in developing and researching technologies in
      the security space. I'm interested in Low Level (Linux, Low Level
      Exploitation) and High Level (Cloud, Networking, AI) technologies
      alike. Skilled in Go, Python and Rust, I approach technical
      challenges with practical and effective solutions.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2>Current Role</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Currently, I work in the <strong>CTO Office at Orca Security</strong
      > as a
      <strong>Senior Software Engineer & Security Researcher</strong> within
      the CTO Innovation Team (reporting to the CTO). My work involves developing
      new projects from scratch.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2>Previous Experience</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Previously, I served in the <strong
        >Israel Defense Forces (Unit Matzov)</strong
      > for over 5 years. My last role there was <strong
        >Innovation Lead</strong
      > in the CTO Office (June 2023 - June 2024), where I led innovation efforts
      focused on the Cloud Security landscape of the IDF.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2>Top Skills</h2>
    <ul class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="logos:python"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Python
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="logos:go"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Go
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="logos:c-plusplus"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> C++
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="logos:rust"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Rust
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="mdi:cloud-lock"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Cloud Security
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="mdi:shield-key"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Identity Security
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="mdi:api"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> API Security
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="mdi:shield-bug"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Application Security
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="mdi:target-account"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Red Teaming
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="mdi:magnify-scan"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Vulnerability Research
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2>Personal Traits</h2>
    <ul class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2">
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="mdi:hammer-wrench"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Hard Worker
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="mdi:rocket-launch"
          class="inline-block h-5 w-5 mr-1 align-middle"
        /> Ambitious
      </li>
      <li>
        <Icon
          name="mdi:lightbulb-on"
